name: Alec Bradley - White Gold - Robusto
additionalNotes: Alec Bradley fans who place a premium on value have access to White Gold, a mixed-filler blend crafted to keep your bottom dollar intact. An Ecuador Connecticut wrapper blankets a core of Dominican and Nicaraguan tobaccos blended to deliver satisfaction for a minimal investment. Enjoy a profile of toasted nuts with a touch of cream in an everyday value by Alec Bradley.
